<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 col-sm-12">
                <h2 class="mb-4">📢 Important Announcement: Server Hosting Migration</h2>
                <p>Hey everyone! 👋 We have an important update about the future of our Minecraft network.</p>

                <h3 class="mt-5">📦 What’s Happening?</h3>
                <p>Over the next 2–3 weeks, we’ll be migrating all of our servers to a new hosting provider.</p>
                <p>Most migrations will happen quietly with minimal downtime. However, two major components will require scheduled maintenance:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Proxy Server</strong> – the network’s main hub</li>
                    <li><strong>Survival Server</strong> – our largest and most active server, so downtime will be longer</li>
                </ul>
                <p>We’ll announce exact maintenance times soon so you can plan ahead.</p>

                <h3 class="mt-5">✨ Why Are We Moving?</h3>
                <p>This migration allows us to improve the quality, reliability, and performance of our entire network.</p>
                <p>Our goal is to provide a place where you can play, grow, and be encouraged alongside Christ’s people. This upgrade helps us to continue doing that well.</p>

                <h3 class="mt-5">💬 What Does This Mean for the Community?</h3>
                <p>Better hosting comes with increased operational costs.</p>
                <p>As we finalise our 2026 operations budget, we ask you to pray for wisdom as we steward our resources.</p>
                <p>If you feel led, please also prayerfully consider supporting the server by:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Purchasing a rank, or</li>
                    <li>Subscribing to a monthly support tier</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="https://craftingforchrist.net/ranks" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">Support the Server</a>

                <h3 class="mt-5">📊 Financial Transparency</h3>
                <p>In the next 1–2 weeks, we will publish a page outlining our financial status. We aim to update this regularly so our community can stay informed.</p>

                <h3 class="mt-5">🙏 Thank You</h3>
                <p>A big thank-you to our current hosting provider for supporting our network up to this point.</p>
                <p>And thank YOU, our awesome community, for continuing to play, pray, and grow with us. ❤️</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

